  'Produtos/Bônus': `<svg viewBox="0 0 120 72" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect width="120" height="72" rx="4" fill="#0f172a"/><rect x="34" y="6" width="52" height="3" rx="1.5" fill="#fbbf24"/><rect x="6" y="14" width="34" height="50" rx="4" fill="#1e293b"/><rect x="14" y="22" width="18" height="14" rx="2" fill="#fef3c7"/><text x="23" y="32" text-anchor="middle" fill="#f59e0b" font-size="8">🎁</text><rect x="10" y="42" width="26" height="3" rx="1.5" fill="white"/><rect x="11" y="55" width="24" height="3" rx="1.5" fill="#fbbf24"/><rect x="43" y="14" width="34" height="50" rx="4" fill="#1e293b"/><rect x="51" y="22" width="18" height="14" rx="2" fill="#fef3c7"/><text x="60" y="32" text-anchor="middle" fill="#f59e0b" font-size="8">🎁</text><rect x="47" y="42" width="26" height="3" rx="1.5" fill="white"/><rect x="48" y="55" width="24" height="3" rx="1.5" fill="#fbbf24"/><rect x="80" y="14" width="34" height="50" rx="4" fill="#1e293b"/><rect x="88" y="22" width="18" height="14" rx="2" fill="#fef3c7"/><text x="97" y="32" text-anchor="middle" fill="#f59e0b" font-size="8">🎁</text><rect x="84" y="42" width="26" height="3" rx="1.5" fill="white"/><rect x="85" y="55" width="24" height="3" rx="1.5" fill="#fbbf24"/></svg>`,
